00:32:03,615 --> 00:32:04,780
Ini perkara bagus.

506
00:32:05,730 --> 00:32:06,655
Qiyi.

507
00:32:07,995 --> 00:32:11,050
Adakah awak rasa
Sanshang bersikap aneh?

508
00:32:11,290 --> 00:32:11,860
Kenapa?

509
00:32:13,150 --> 00:32:14,035
Entahlah.

510
00:32:15,025 --> 00:32:16,790
Saya rasa dia bersikap aneh.

511
00:32:18,870 --> 00:32:20,455
Terutamanya senyuman dia itu.

512
00:32:21,905 --> 00:32:24,100
Lepas awak cakap, saya pun rasa begitu.

513
00:32:26,515 --> 00:32:28,640
Ayahnya baru meninggal,

514
00:32:29,350 --> 00:32:31,545
dia memerlukan masa
untuk menerima hakikat ini.

515
00:32:45,260 --> 00:32:46,635
Bintang terkenal, Kak Xun

516
00:32:46,695 --> 00:32:48,315
berdating dengan lelaki yang misteri
di hotel.

517
00:32:48,515 --> 00:32:49,655
Interaksi mereka sangat intim.

518
00:32:49,656 --> 00:32:51,240
Percintaan sulit disyaki terdedah.

519
00:32:51,710 --> 00:32:52,295
Biar saya tengok.

520
00:32:58,785 --> 00:33:00,030
Adakah kamu rasa

521
00:33:00,575 --> 00:33:02,760
lelaki ini nampak macam Cikgu Sun?

522
00:33:03,060 --> 00:33:03,955
Cikgu Sun?

523
00:33:06,080 --> 00:33:07,360
Cikgu Sun dan Kak Xun

524
00:33:07,361 --> 00:33:08,910
bukan dari golongan yang sama.

525
00:33:12,330 --> 00:33:14,270
Sanshang pasti ada sesuatu
yang tak kena.

526
00:33:20,040 --> 00:33:21,040
Amboi!

527
00:33:21,955 --> 00:33:23,810
Teman lelaki Kak Xun telah terdedah.

528
00:33:24,030 --> 00:33:25,180
Siapa?

529
00:33:25,655 --> 00:33:27,145
Teman lelaki Kak Xun.

530
00:33:27,465 --> 00:33:28,220
Teman lelaki siapa?

531
00:33:28,490 --> 00:33:29,220
Kak Xun.

532
00:33:29,435 --> 00:33:30,145
Siapa Kak Xun?

533
00:33:30,215 --> 00:33:31,330
Cepat tengok Weibo.

534
00:33:31,625 --> 00:33:32,355
Apa itu Weibo?

535
00:33:34,260 --> 00:33:34,835
Ke tepi!

536
00:33:35,430 --> 00:33:36,380
Awak ini ketinggalan zaman!

537
00:33:36,400 --> 00:33:39,880
(Esok, awak lapang?)

538
00:33:41,480 --> 00:33:44,400
(Esok, awak ada urusan tak?)

539
00:33:45,440 --> 00:33:52,040
(Qiyi. Du Ang)

540
00:33:53,600 --> 00:34:00,160
(Ada apa-apakah?)

541
00:34:00,880 --> 00:34:08,640
(Esok hari jadi saya.)

542
00:34:09,120 --> 00:34:12,400
(Macam mana awak menyambutnya?)

543
00:34:12,956 --> 00:34:15,480
(Makan dan bergembira.
Awak lapang?)

544
00:34:15,862 --> 00:34:20,320
(Lapang.)

545
00:34:20,400 --> 00:34:25,240
(Restoran Lao Cun)

546
00:34:25,320 --> 00:34:26,034
(Okey)

547
00:34:42,980 --> 00:34:43,350
Du Ang.

548
00:34:43,515 --> 00:34:44,345
Selamat hari jadi.

549
00:34:49,090 --> 00:34:49,650
Qiyi.

550
00:34:51,340 --> 00:34:52,570
Sekarang, perasaan saya

551
00:34:54,010 --> 00:34:55,260
seperti bunga mawar ini.

552
00:34:57,895 --> 00:34:58,745
Awak tengah buat apa?

553
00:34:59,690 --> 00:35:00,170
Saya...

554
00:35:01,425 --> 00:35:02,770
Awak ini teruk.

555
00:35:02,890 --> 00:35:04,475
Tak beritahu saya
tentang sambutan hari jadi awak.

556
00:35:05,115 --> 00:35:06,435
Mari kita pergi makan.

557
00:35:06,750 --> 00:35:07,240
Sekejap.

558
00:35:08,200 --> 00:35:09,235
Mengapa kamu di sini?

559
00:35:10,890 --> 00:35:11,730
Kalau begitu, kami pergi dari sini.

560
00:35:11,995 --> 00:35:12,935
Qiyi, jom.

561
00:35:13,220 --> 00:35:13,640
Ayuh.

562
00:35:13,641 --> 00:35:14,200
Tunggu!

563
00:35:16,615 --> 00:35:18,230
Kita pergi makan bersama-sama.

564
00:35:18,690 --> 00:35:19,260
Merayulah.

565
00:35:26,160 --> 00:35:27,315
Tolonglah, Kak Kaixin.

566
00:35:29,180 --> 00:35:29,985
Baiklah.

567
00:35:29,986 --> 00:35:30,335
Jom.

568
00:35:30,410 --> 00:35:30,745
Jom.

569
00:35:40,680 --> 00:35:41,545
Namun, saya...

570
00:35:42,935 --> 00:35:44,135
Saya tiada air mata.

571
00:35:45,635 --> 00:35:46,460
Alam semesta

572
00:35:47,460 --> 00:35:48,810
juga tiada air mata.

573
00:35:49,630 --> 00:35:50,815
Apa kegunaan air mata pula?

574
00:35:53,090 --> 00:35:54,550
Kita hanya ada ribut angin,

575
00:35:54,615 --> 00:35:56,655
petir dan kilat!

576
00:35:56,915 --> 00:35:58,895
Kita tiada hujan yang berlanjutan.

577
00:36:00,075 --> 00:36:01,320
Ini ialah keazaman saya.

578
00:36:01,945 --> 00:36:03,280
Ini ialah keazaman alam semesta.

579
00:36:04,825 --> 00:36:06,115
Bergeraklah, angin.

580
00:36:06,595 --> 00:36:07,875
Mengaumlah, petir.

581
00:36:08,030 --> 00:36:09,355
Bersinarlah, kilat!

582
00:36:09,830 --> 00:36:12,310
Musnahkan perkara-perkara yang

583
00:36:12,550 --> 00:36:13,595
tidur dalam kegelapan!

584
00:36:13,820 --> 00:36:14,820
Musnahkan!

585
00:36:21,920 --> 00:36:24,281
(Bilik Vila)

586
00:36:25,570 --> 00:36:26,195
Qiyi.

587
00:36:26,555 --> 00:36:26,970
Duduk.

588
00:36:33,025 --> 00:36:33,635
Terima kasih.

589
00:36:37,370 --> 00:36:38,360
Saya duduk di sini.

590
00:36:39,200 --> 00:36:39,740
Ke tepi.

591
00:36:41,875 --> 00:36:42,380
Qiyi.

592
00:36:42,930 --> 00:36:43,910
Nak makan apa? Pesanlah.

593
00:36:45,000 --> 00:36:46,490
Bilik Pondok, dua orang.

594
00:36:46,750 --> 00:36:47,740
Tiga lauk itu, seperti biasa.

595
00:36:47,840 --> 00:36:48,615
Baik.

596
00:36:57,160 --> 00:36:59,630
Saya mahu makan
"Saya dilahirkan dengan bakat".

597
00:37:00,595 --> 00:37:02,900
Awak sesuai untuk makan
"Pemandangan indah tak dapat ditutup".

598
00:37:04,975 --> 00:37:06,465
Maksud awak, saya cantik?

599
00:37:07,570 --> 00:37:08,720
"Rotan layu, pokok tua,
burung gagak pada waktu senja".

600
00:37:11,220 --> 00:37:12,465
Qiyi, awak pesanlah.

601
00:37:15,915 --> 00:37:17,475
Inilah tempat yang selalu awak datang?

602
00:37:18,430 --> 00:37:20,060
Saya ingin ajak awak datang selama ini.

603
00:37:20,970 --> 00:37:21,550
Qiyi.

604
00:37:23,040 --> 00:37:23,840
Terima kasih.

605
00:37:27,415 --> 00:37:28,410
Siapa mereka?

606
00:37:29,180 --> 00:37:30,615
Bawa pengawal peribadi pula.

607
00:37:31,035 --> 00:37:31,505
Siapa?

608
00:37:31,915 --> 00:37:32,795
Siapa bawa pengawal peribadi?

609
00:38:05,763 --> 00:38:11,273
♪Saya memendamkan
perasaan diri dalam hati♪

610
00:38:11,274 --> 00:38:16,837
♪Tak berani untuk mendedahkan
cinta saya terhadap awak♪

611
00:38:20,523 --> 00:38:25,955
♪Dalam percintaan,
fikiran saya selalu bercelaru♪

612
00:38:25,956 --> 00:38:31,784
♪Tak pernah bertemu dengan lelaki
yang menggoncangkan dunia saya♪

613
00:38:33,923 --> 00:38:38,010
♪Jika jarak kita semakin dekat♪

614
00:38:38,011 --> 00:38:41,248
♪Inilah yang meruntun hati♪

615
00:38:41,249 --> 00:38:45,402
♪Biarpun ini kali terakhir♪

616
00:38:45,403 --> 00:38:51,851
♪Saya nak buktikan keberanian saya
untuk memegang tangan awak♪

617
00:38:52,803 --> 00:38:57,204
♪Lihatlah kita yang berkembang subur
di tengah-tengah pentas♪

618
00:38:57,205 --> 00:39:01,063
♪Langkah kita bagai impian cinta♪

619
00:39:01,064 --> 00:39:07,501
♪Setiap nota muzik dan rentak
wujud atas sebab awak♪

620
00:39:07,502 --> 00:39:11,566
♪Dengarlah lagu merdu
yang kita nyanyi bersama♪

621
00:39:11,963 --> 00:39:15,543
♪Dalam setiap detik♪

622
00:39:15,923 --> 00:39:20,046
♪Keharuan yang tidak akan lenyap♪

623
00:39:20,683 --> 00:39:24,202
♪Dan kekal dalam ingatan kita
buat selama-lamanya♪

624
00:39:25,883 --> 00:39:31,846
♪Keharuan yang tidak akan lenyap♪

